Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm?\NDoes that mean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, argh,\Nit's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop)\NSweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic,\Nsomething's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait,\None of those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that\Nflying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth ramen\Nwith wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence,\Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:00:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away,\Nin total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll be\Nlaughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.49,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit\N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits\N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels,\Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just called on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... then, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not asleep, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't said anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Question of Motivation"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my English textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.09,0:02:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go\Nborrow it from Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had English class too\Ntoday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's because you're so careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to check the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa tends to\Nforget a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Konata,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you hardly forget stuff like textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty reliable\Nabout things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave all the textbooks\Nin the classroom in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!\NYou're not reliable at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you leave all\Nthe textbooks here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't review what\Nwe learned in class at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you leave\Nall the textbooks here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the night before the exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}is good at doing\Nthe one-night study plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why I always\Nforget my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, it's not that you're\Nforgetting the homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't have the will to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So can I see this afternoon's\NJapanese class homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wonder one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you two are in the same class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you have Miyuki\Nshow you her homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}is just such a good person\Nthat it's hard to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you don't\Nunderstand this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda get it, but that isn't\Na satisfactory answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit tardy as a result\Nof helping someone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually spend my time\Nwith this person,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just couldn't bring myself\Nto say goodbye today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "I'm fine, so let's disband,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when the other five members\Ngot what they wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that one person is\Nthe only one who couldn't get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it just leaves such\Na bad taste in your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were in a party for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we said, "At times like this,\Nwe need to help each other out,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and cheered each other up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, having good comrades\Nreally is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you spent all night playing\Na net game again last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On and on, after I logged out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi! Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of the shopping strip,\Na girl bumped into me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that girl suddenly grabbed\Nmy hand and started to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, upon listening to\Nwhat she had to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,apparently she stole a piece\Nof {\i1}taiyaki {\i0}and was on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "Why do I have\Nto run away with her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get involved in all of this?"\NBut since I couldn't help it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we entered a café to escape\Nfrom the {\i1}taiyaki {\i0}shop owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uguu, there are so many places\Nin this story to nitpick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a bad thing to\Npoint out all the flaws,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both as a teacher and\Nas a human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a summer cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Izumi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ma'am, I'm sorry,\NI'd like sick leave today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, playing games\Ntoo much again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really use the same trick\Nover and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I want to take sick leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to say that you've\Ncaught a summer cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rainy season is already over,\Nand we've got good weather now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be saying\Nyou're sluggish all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so hurry up and get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, yesterday, I really felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was being treated like\Nthe boy who cried wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, are you all right already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my fever's gone down,\Nbut my throat still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that means that you breathe\Nthrough your mouth, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course she'd breathe\Nthrough her mouth too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it usually through your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but the percentage in which
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan {\i0}breathes through\Nher mouth is higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you know, when the\Ncold virus enters your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get a throat cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when it goes in through your\Nnose, you get a sinus cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those that get\Na throat cold, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have a higher rate of getting\Nthe virus in from their throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, at times like this, how\Nabout we let Miyuki-{\i1}san {\i0}handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagami? About that\Nbirthday party today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how about we do it\Nat my place after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so hot I can't\Nmove one more step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame... I'm baking cookies\Nat my house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, hurry over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Tsukasa\Nand one other person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abbreviate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday,\NKagami-{\i1}san{\i0}, Tsukasa-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is something really simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought it would\Nmake a nice gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matching earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about all sorts of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but couldn't come up with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I give you two\Nsomething as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A brigade leader's armband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to put on\Nsomething like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd look\Nperfect in it, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it suits you better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To Heart{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was expensive!\NTreat it well when you wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to make us both cosplay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that different from\Nthe uniforms we wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a problem if it's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Another problem\Nis when it's too smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's someone\Nelse's birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't you hold back a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cookies Tsukasa bakes\Nreally are good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I helped out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was teaching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, but upon hearing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like there are tasty ones and\Nnot-so-tasty ones mixed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is one of yours, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're at it,\Nhave some cake too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Kagamin works diligently\Nonly on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, don't you end up arguing\Nover how to cut the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like when you cut it\Ninto many pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what to do with the\Nstrawberries on top,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or who gets to eat the\Nchocolate sign plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you like those sign plates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I went out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it's not {\i1}moe\N{\i0}when it's Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strawberry is so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Is there\Nsome cake on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just found another charming\Npoint about Kagamin, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You're really\Nsounding like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer vacation already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, the pool,\Nsummer festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any must-dos out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of summer, there is\Nthe twice-a-year festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The war zone in Ariake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\Nit's gotta be Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, that's only for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Comiket?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for certain people\Nthere are all sorts of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like going home for the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, do you have a staple thing\Nto do during the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we're planning to go\Noverseas again this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! Did you say again?!\NDamn you bourgeois...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that yogurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bourgeois?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you started\Nworking in a cosplay café,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't those places only hire\Npeople with good figures and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been lamenting my lack\Nof breasts for all this time too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:57.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Flat"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:09:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you know, in a certain \Ngame, they were saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A flat chest is\Na status symbol! It's rare!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:09.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Small Breasts as a Status Symbol\NRare and Valuable"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are needs of\Nthat sort as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a valuable person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how you can be\Nthat confident thanks to a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, maybe I'm fine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... it's almost finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right,\Nplaying games so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could channel that passion,\Nif only a little, into studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure your grades\Nwould improve quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's that easily swayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if some game that\Nlauded studies came out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something incredible might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those {\i1}moe\N{\i0}quiz drills out already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many\Nteenage crimes lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When things like that happen,\Nthey ask all the neighbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they always say something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He was usually such a quiet boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he never seemed to be\Nthe type that would do that."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that shows all the more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that superficial personalities\Nreally aren't of any use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to commit a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I always thought that she would\Ndo something like this someday,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be exactly what I would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot, I don't feel like\Ndoing anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely understand\Nhow you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you always have\None excuse or another
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to not feel like doing\Nanything all year long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hiiragi family"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up? How's your\Nexam studies going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just cleaning up\Nmy room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when you're\Npressed for time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you just get the urge\Nto clean up and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel,\Nbut do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do at least a little today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a 30-minute break.\NMy concentration doesn't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, it's already time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 more minutes... 30 more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for {\i1}Haruhi {\i0}to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nagato's long scene\Nthe production staff cutting corners?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ya___oto really\Nisn't much lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're flaming away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already 2 AM...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really get to it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sleep a bit, and study some\Nearly in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to get up at 5:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sleep for three hours right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I wasted all my time\Nlast night with manga and anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like you, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Konata, you have\Nstrange tastes in manga and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only read boys' magazines, and\Nyour games are mainly dating sims.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's always read manga\Nand played a lot of games,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think that's what influenced me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was little, I've been there\Nwatching him read or play.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand\Nthe boys' magazines,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what kind of father plays\Ndating sims with cute girls
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of his daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With both a father and\Na daughter like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't your mom feel bad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we don't have\Na mom in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died when I was really young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I always do\Nthe household chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do much more\Nthan you can, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go stating\Nsomething unnecessary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the middle of\Na conversation on a hard topic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at most cooking,\Nright, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I'm good at it,\Nbut I love to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems rich, so she might be\Nbad at doing household chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I only help out\Nevery so often,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not too good\Nat household chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit embarrassing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Miyuki is too good\Nin all other aspects,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which makes her sense\Nof quality different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So her "not so good"\Nshouldn't be taken literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says she lives alone,\Nbut she really has a slacker image.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this day and age, you can get by\Neven if you can't cook at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are convenience stores and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I properly do my housework!\NI can handle as much as anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make jokes\Nthat we can't tell are jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tsukasa still has my dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, sorry, but can I\Nhave my dictionary back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about cleaning my room\Na little to change my mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us at work
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are supposed to think of new\Nmenu items for the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they have those?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, have you given up\Non studying for the exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about having something\Nreally spicy because it's hot out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and going for ultra-spicy ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about something that's\Nmore fitting for a café?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, an ultra-spicy parfait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stop with that knee-jerk\Nreflex way of thinking already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't our school have\Nany swimming classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a pool, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good for me that we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I cannot open\Nmy eyes underwater,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't swim that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so embarrassing to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weaknesses, each and\Nevery time, are so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the summer Comp-Fest\Nis finally going to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I started\Nmy job just for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival... Everything about\Nit brings up memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that old routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when customers join in\Nand get all energetic and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get the feeling that you're making\Nthe festival rowdier together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could turn even\Na little of that passion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,towards what goes on at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think I'll read a book\Nuntil I get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just happen to have\Nbought a new book, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did I not get sleepy,\Nit's already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I'm tired and\Nready to go to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Silent Mode"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know to turn the power off\Nnear the priority seats
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it has something to do\Nwith pacemakers and stuff, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is talking on the phone\Nbasically not allowed in trains?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it because when you talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a nuisance to\Neveryone around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, aren't there people\Nout there that talk too loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they're not on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of age or gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do some\Npriestess thing like New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don't do that kind\Nof stuff in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nit's already that time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Aren't you\Non a diet right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it was because of\Nfatigue from all the exam studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I got on the scale yesterday\NI had lost a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm like, it's all right, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So quick... Or rather, so weak-willed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my weight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gained it all back in,\Nlike, the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you put yourself off\Nguard and ate too many snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that a senryu poem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:45.56,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's my weight again! \NI gained it all back in, like,\Nthe blink of an eye!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much\Ndifference in appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you gain or lose\Na kilogram or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she look\Nso ecstatic or depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a matter of a few kilograms?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why girls are so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are supposed to be a girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This week, {\i1}Lucky Channel\N{\i0}has started up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have all of you been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Akira Kogami,\Nalways at 120% energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This week...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nyoron! Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minoru Shiraishi, the assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk over me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a kid's errand,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so learn to do your job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want to quit\Nthis job that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'm so sorry,\NI'll do my best, my very best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this time... Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is big news for all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The big request for\NAkira's Fashion Project
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the November issue of {\i1}Comptiq{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got this many letters\Nfrom all of you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that project also involved\Nsomeone besides Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all of your entries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am mammoth happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't get those '80s references.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, from all these entries,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to introduce the ideas that\Nwere chosen after a strict ruling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the Akira Fashion\NProject from "Cherry"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Satte City, Saitama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... "Kagami looks good\Nin twin pigtails,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so how about you try\Ntwin pigtails as well, Akira?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twin pigtails, huh--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Long hair\Nis the life of a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And splitting it in two is, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,giving it a very elegant\Nlook to it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing it or not, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the length of your hair\Nmakes it impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like making your hair\Nlonger automatically makes it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It gets heavy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's almost showing, so, please, lower...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It gets harder to shampoo too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, right now,\Nit's not the in thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say "guys like girls\Nwith long hair" so easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's about the people who're inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but do they know exactly how much time, \Nmoney, and effort go into its upkeep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:06.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--The people who are inside it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's not about you, Akira-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Furthermore, despite the effort, \Nnobody notices the difference...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you listening to me? Please, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what would I be\Nlike in twin pigtails?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest will be on my homepage,\Nor talked out on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you guys listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll wait for ordinary mail too! Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then, please look forward \Nto the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that attitude earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept snapping at me!\NWhat was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get irritated because\NI corrected you in the beginning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just wondering\Nif people nowadays
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would catch the Nori-P reference...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. Let's have\Na new, fresh feeling to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear they're holding an audition\Nfor the role of Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?\NThis is the first I've heard of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you can apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm going to apply?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But I'm the actual person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The actual what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you're amazing!\NYou can sing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's limited to anime songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use various types of voices,\Nand sing very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fundamental law\Nof singing anime songs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to perfectly mimic the original singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I guess I'll sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to sing, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The title came up a while ago,\Nbut it was a song that I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, you don't know this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice what you preach, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've heard this song before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching the drama series\Nwith me until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the movie version after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an old guy or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:50.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Goodbye is not a word of farewell ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amongst my sisters, she's the best singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:57.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ But a distant promise for\Nthe day we meet again ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.12,0:23:06.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Even if regret is left in the place\Nwhere the dream used to be ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:13.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It only leaves the heart in the cold ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.34,0:23:21.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Just like this, for \Nhowever many hours ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:27.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I would like to hold you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:30.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with\Nthe next episode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Golden Week was
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an industry term named so\Nbecause during this time period,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of moviegoers\Nincreases dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: The Famous Shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:43.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Famous Shooter"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
